Olga tried to solve an equation step by step.

$\begin{align}
\dfrac14\left(\dfrac13k+9\right)&=6
\\\\
\dfrac13k+9&=24&\green{\text{Step } 1}
\\\\
\dfrac13k&=15&\blue{\text{Step } 2}
\\\\
k&=5&\purple{\text{Step } 3}
\end{align}$

**Find Olga's mistake.**

[[☃ radio 1]]
